    "year": 1990,
    "launchDate": "1990",
    "description": "1990 American crewed spaceflight to deploy Ulysses",
    "extract": "STS-41 was the 36th Space Shuttle mission and the eleventh mission of the Space Shuttle Discovery. The four-day mission had a primary objective of launching the Ulysses probe as part of the \"International Solar Polar Mission\" (ISPM).",
