    "launchDate": "1991",
    "description": "1991 American crewed spaceflight for the Department of Defense",
    "extract": "STS-39 was the twelfth mission of the NASA Space Shuttle Discovery, and the 40th orbital shuttle mission overall. The primary purpose of the mission was to conduct a variety of payload experiments for the U.S. Department of Defense (DoD).",
    "patchFile": "STS-39 patch.svg",
