    "launchDate": "1997",
    "description": "1997 American crewed spaceflight to ''Mir''",
    "extract": "STS-86 was a Space Shuttle Atlantis mission to the Mir space station. This was the last Atlantis mission before it was taken out of service temporarily for maintenance and upgrades, including the glass cockpit.",
    "patchFile": "Sts-86-patch.svg",
